name: ShutUpAndListen Tee (Black or White)
description:
ShutUpAndListen

To celebrate our exclusive SUALMIX series we bring you the ShutUpAndListen Tee.

Printed on full weight cotton (Fruit Of The Loom) these Limited Edition Tees are available in Black and White.

Featuring a ShutUpAndListen design on the front, a theSNT logo on the back and we loved the design Marie Err did for us in Issue 06 we used it for the inside collar print.

A snip at only £12 with FREE STICKERS - of course

http://www.mixcloud.com/theSNT_Zine/


Also available in White, girls sizes and sweatshirts (black) - email contact (at) theSNT.co.uk if you want one.
